KV SSD linux kernel driver package
==================================

This package includes kernel driver that operates with KV SSD.



Driectory structure
===================
kernel_driver
      | - README
      | - kernel_v3.10
      | - kernel_v4.9.5
      | - kernel_v4.13
      | - kernel_v4.15


How-to build and install kernel driver
======================================
1) build
cd PDK/driver/PCIe/kernel_driver/kernel_v<version>/
make clean
make all

2) install
cd PDK/driver/PCIe/kernel_driver/kernel_v<version>/
sudo ./re_insmod

